{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the magical world of Kleks Academy, where imagination knows no limits. As a new student, you'll create your own unique avatar and learn to harness extraordinary powers like size-shifting, long leaps, telekinesis, and even flight! The Academy serves as a gateway to legendary fairy tales, from <i>Jack and the Beanstalk</i> to <i>Little Red Riding Hood</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore, solve puzzles, and interact with beloved characters as you relive these timeless stories from a fresh perspective. Each world presents challenges that can be tackled in multiple ways depending on the skills you acquire. Can you unlock the mysteries of these magical lands and return to the Academy ready to face the ultimate threat?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by the whimsical adventure of <i>Kleks Academy</i>, this action-adventure platformer is built for players of all ages. Customize your character, embark on cooperative multiplayer missions, and immerse yourself in a world where imagination is the key to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a magical academy and iconic fairy tale worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master unique skills like telekinesis and flight to solve puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your character\u2019s appearance and abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play solo or in online co-op with up to 4 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience multiple endings and paths in each level based on your choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No combat: solve challenges by manipulating objects and using your powers creatively</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to protect the Academy from the looming darkness?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=172985